name: Acceleration Aerator
description:
Celebrate this. Being drunk in love after live music is kind of like dying. An album called x and y made a cover band named Coldplay in Strings real for the first time. 

Because Coldplay was mentioned in the list
of the greatest bands of all time next to 
Aerosmith

And the best thing to follow it with is only David Bowie
RIP at 69 in 2016

Just a bit of time before the next wave hits the radio in my auditorium. Radio level music is a rarity these days. All rock records miss the quarter beat signature in one way or another.
